serve-this
==========

Serve the contents of the current directory,
like it was running on a server.

Example
=======

  $ serve-this
  *****
  serving ~/some/directory on port 9292
  
  $ serve-this --rackup
  *****
  creating a Gemfile and config.ru
  this directory is now a rack app!

Push it to Heroku!
==================

  Gemfile
  
    source :rubygems
    gem "serve-this"
    
  config.ru

    require 'rubygems'
    require 'bundler'
    Bundler.require

    run ServeThis.from(Dir.pwd)

